'''Streysel Island''' was an island that was part of the [[Vaynai Archipelago]], which was the main area of habitable surface land on the [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] resort [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Vaynai/Legends|Vaynai]]. The island was owned by the [[Crime lord/Legends|crime lord]], [[Gallo Memm]], and was also home to the [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Oneron Fil'vye]], who owned and operated the shipping company [[Fil'vye Transport]].<ref name="The Vaynai Archipelago">{{GamerCite|8|The Vaynai Archipelago}}</ref>

